OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fspread northeast during this evening
OL,7,Fand in the early hours. Drier weather
OL,8,Fdeveloping later in the night with
OL,9,Fclear periods along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FA mainly dry and cloudy day,
OL,12,Fsome patchy rain across the southwest.
OL,13,FBright at times along the east coast.
OL,14,FMild.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,17,Fand mild on Wednesday with rain at
OL,18,Ftimes, drier in the east. Breezy with
OL,19,Fshowers on Thursday. Rain for a time
OL,20,FFriday morning, showers later.
